entities.aonHelper/DreamLockBlock.attributes.description.useVanillaKeys=Whether this Dream Lock Block can be unlocked by vanilla keys.
entities.aonHelper/DreamLockBlock.attributes.description.dzhakeHelperKeySettings=Describes which Dzhake Helper Custom Key Groups (if any) this Dream Lock Block can be unlocked by.\nLeft empty: this Dream Lock Block cannot be unlocked by Dzhake Helper keys.\n*: this Dream Lock Block can be unlocked by any Dzhake Helper key.\nAny integer: this Dream Lock Block can only be unlocked by a Dzhake Helper key with the specified Group. 

