triggers.aonHelper/ParallaxFadeTrigger.placements.name.parallax_fade=Parallax Fade
triggers.aonHelper/ParallaxFadeTrigger.placements.description.parallax_fade=A trigger that allows fading the color and alpha of Parallax stylegrounds.
triggers.aonHelper/ParallaxFadeTrigger.attributes.description.colorFrom=The start color of the affected stylegrounds. Leave empty to not affect the color of the affected stylegrounds.
